channel.title: What?!
channel.description:
Ok well I am making a private server and well I got everything and I am using whitescape and well so I want to log in and then i start up the RunServer for whitescape then start up moparscape but its not my server how it should be it is still moparscape...I watched a video tutorial and I did everything in it and when I hit moparscape it should have a java thing on the page beside it...but mine isent there so...anyone know why and how i can fix that so I can start my server??
Please and Thanks!

item.title: What?!
item.dc:creator: @Word8 Word8
item.description:
@Word8 wrote:

not sure what your asking but … if you have your server ready to go and everything do these steps

  1. click Runserver
  2. Open Mopar
  3. (don’t click start server … that might what you have been doing) just click login the put the user name you wish
  4. have fun on your server

if that doesn’t work then try putting your server ip for new server on mopar?

sorry if this didn’t help
